Definition: a hypothetical three-dimensional visual world created by a computer
Example: user wears special goggles and fiber optic gloves etc., and can enter and move about in this world and interact with objects as if inside it
Synonyms: computer_game, a, hypothetical, three-dimensional, visual, world, created, by, computer, user, wears, special, goggles, and, fiber, optic, gloves, etc, can, enter, move, about, in, this, interact, with, objects, as, if, inside, it
Category: noun.act
